### Commands

```
sc.exe create cpuz.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\cpuz.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start cpuz.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
